01:23:11.736 --> 01:23:13.947
Opet?

01:23:13.989 --> 01:23:17.367
Mislio sam da si bistar-
oštrouman, inteligentan.

01:23:17.450 --> 01:23:21.414
Dugmad i sapun od ljudi?
To bi bilo čudo!

01:23:21.497 --> 01:23:23.958
Poverovao si u to?

